manifests.contents:
bin = []
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[package]
name = "siege-api"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
base64 = "0.21.0"
derive-getters = "0.2.0"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.24"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.15"
features = ["json", "rustls-tls"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.158"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.strum]
version = "0.24.1"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.26.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.3.0"
features = ["serde"]

[dev-dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0.95"

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "siege_api"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]

bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "siege-bot"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "siege-bot"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Oliver Fleckenstein <oliverfl@live.dk>"]
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = false

[dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1.68"
duplicate = "1.0.0"
serde_json = "1.0.95"
strum = "0.24.1"
thiserror = "1.0.40"
tracing = "0.1.37"
uuid = "1.3.0"

[dependencies.serenity]
version = "0.11.5"
features = ["client", "gateway", "rustls_backend", "model", "utils"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.siege-api]
path = "../siege-api"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.26.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.16"
features = ["env-filter"]
